org.springframework.web.client.reactive

类 ExchangeFilterFunctions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.web.client.reactive.ExchangeFilterFunctions

  • public abstract class ExchangeFilterFunctions
extends Object
    Implementations of ExchangeFilterFunction that provide various useful request filter operations, such as basic authentication, error handling, etc.
    从以下版本开始:
    5.0
    作者:
    Rob Winch, Arjen Poutsma

    • 方法详细资料

      • clientError

        public static ExchangeFilterFunction clientError()
        Return a filter that will publish a WebClientException when the ClientResponse has a 4xx status code.
        返回:
        the ExchangeFilterFunction that publishes a WebClientException when the response has a client error

      • serverError

        public static ExchangeFilterFunction serverError()
        Return a filter that will publish a WebClientException if the ClientResponse has a 5xx status code.
        返回:
        the ExchangeFilterFunction that publishes a WebClientException when the response has a server error

      • clientOrServerError

        public static ExchangeFilterFunction clientOrServerError()
        Return a filter that will publish a WebClientException if the ClientResponse has a 4xx or 5xx status code.
        返回:
        the ExchangeFilterFunction that publishes a WebClientException when the response has a client or server error

      • errorPredicate

        public static ExchangeFilterFunction errorPredicate(Predicate<ClientResponse> predicate)
        Return a filter that will publish a WebClientException if the response satisfies the given predicate function.
        参数:
        predicate - the predicate to test the response with
        返回:
        the ExchangeFilterFunction that publishes a WebClientException when predicate returns true

      • errorMapper

        public static ExchangeFilterFunction errorMapper(Function<ClientResponse,Optional<? extends Throwable>> mapper)
        Return a filter that maps the response to a potential error. Exceptions returned by mapper will be published as signal in the Mono<ClientResponse> return value.
        参数:
        mapper - the function that maps from response to optional error
        返回:
        the ExchangeFilterFunction that propagates the errors provided by mapper

      • basicAuthentication

        public static ExchangeFilterFunction basicAuthentication(String username,
                                                         String password)
        Return a filter that adds an Authorization header for HTTP Basic Authentication.
        参数:
        username - the username to use
        password - the password to use
        返回:
        the ExchangeFilterFunction that adds the Authorization header
